                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">对爻辞有很细腻的分析。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1045862821">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1045862821" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1045862821" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1045862821">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/58268924/">谁懂易经</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-05-27</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">你虽然是日本人，但对易学宣传的贡献比他的发源地人民所有人家起来，还要多</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1036577218">
